// import phoneimg from "../../images/phone.png"

                    <Box mt="5" bg="white" width="120px" height="100px"></Box>

                    <Box mt="5" bg="white" width="120px" height="100px"></Box>
                    <Box mt="5" bg="white" width="120px" height="100px"></Box>

                </Flex>
            </Box>
        </>

}
